title: Kuwait Reverse Repo Rate
description: Reverse Repo Rate in Kuwait remained unchanged at 2.38 percent in October from 2.38 percent in September of 2022. Reverse Repo Rate in Kuwait averaged 1.92 percent from 2005 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 5.87 percent in July of 2006 and a record low of 0.75 percent in August of 2009. This page provides - Kuwait Reverse Repo Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Kuwait
